FOIA Case Report Information
The physician assessed the following events with respect to Tacrolimus: 
 - Progressive multifocal leukoencephalopathy (seriousness: Death; causality: Possible).
The author noted the case underscores the possible influence of conversion of immunosuppressive treatment with 
reactivation of PML.
No further information is expected.